PMID== 1528638
TI  == isolation and properties of the capnocytophaga ochracea bacteriocin.
AB  == a bacteriocin from a subgingival plaque isolate of capnocytophaga ochracea was purified and characterized. it was isolated from cell extract and had a molecular weight of 100,000. streptococcus sanguis, streptococcus mitis, streptococcus mutans and propionibacterium acnes were susceptible to the bacteriocin.
